  "description": "Bailian-powered unified creative studio — built-in Wan/Qwen image generation + HappyHorse 1.0 (t2v / i2v / r2v / video-edit) + Wan 2.6/2.7 + digital-human (photo speak / video relip / video reface / pose drive / avatar compose) + CosyVoice & Edge-TTS + storyboard long-video pipeline. Single backend (Aliyun DashScope), OSS-backed.",
  "display_name_zh": "快乐马工作室",
  "display_name_en": "HappyHorse Studio",
  "description_i18n": {
    "zh": "基于阿里云百炼的一体化创作工作室 — 内置万相/千问生图 + HappyHorse 1.0（文生 / 图生 / 参考生 / 视频编辑）+ 万相 2.6/2.7 + 数字人 5 模式 + CosyVoice & Edge-TTS + 长视频分镜拼接，统一 OSS 签名 URL。",
    "en": "Bailian-powered unified creative studio — built-in Wan/Qwen image generation + HappyHorse 1.0 (t2v / i2v / r2v / video-edit) + Wan 2.6/2.7 + 5 digital-human modes + CosyVoice & Edge-TTS + storyboard long-video pipeline, single DashScope backend with OSS signed URLs."
  },
  "icon": "icon.svg",
  "author": "OpenAkita",
